dana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">720</span></span></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/digitalocean/go-qemu\">go-qemu</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/digitalocean/go-qemu\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">585</span></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"commercial-integrations\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#commercial-integrations\" aria-label=\"commercial integrations permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Commercial integrations</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://bill.do\">Bill.do</a> - Free DigitalOcean billing monitoring and insights tool</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://hostlaunch.io\">HostLaunch</a> - Launch a hosting company based on DigitalOcean and ServerPilot.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://simplebackups.io\">SimpleBackups</a> - Tool for scheduling DigitalOcean backups (files &#x26; databases) on auto-pilot.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://snapshooter.io/digitalocean\">SnapShooter</a> - Tool for taking Daily to Hourly backups of Droplets and Volumes</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://weap.io\">Weap.io</a> - Hourly to Daily DigitalOcean backups. Tool for scheduling more frequent DigitalOcean backups</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"community-oss-projects\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#community-oss-projects\" aria-label=\"community oss projects permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Community OSS projects</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/f/do-sshuttle\">do-sshuttle</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/f/do-sshuttle\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">66</span></span></a> - Transparent Proxying via sshuttle to DigitalOcean Droplet.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/qmx/drophosts\">drophosts</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/qmx/drophosts\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1</span></span></a> - Update <code class=\"language-text\">/etc/hosts</code> with peer droplets.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/tam7t/droplan\">droplan</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/tam7t/droplan\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">70</span></span></a> - Manage iptable rules for the private interface on DigitalOcean droplets.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/theforeman/foreman-digitalocean\">foreman-digitalocean</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/theforeman/foreman-digitalocean\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">28</span></span></a> - Plugin to enable management of DigitalOcean droplets in Foreman.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shiva-hack/ghost-digitalocean\">ghost-digitalocean</a><a data-role